title: The Interplanetary Surplus Male and Amazon Women of Outer Space
description:
The Interplanetary Surplus Male and Amazon Women of Outer Space (2003 - USA)

Adventure / Science Fiction
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0347250/


A film by Sam Firstenberg, Cannon and Nu Image regular and director of classics like American Ninja, Cyborg Cop, Riverbend, Ninja III, American Samurai, Avenging Force, Breakin' 2: Electric Boogaloo and many, many more. Something strange happened to Sam Firstenberg in the early 2000s. A guy who churned out very entertaining B-movies for two decades suddenly stopped doing them. We can only speculate that it was thanks to this piece of work.

Every 100 years a race of alien amazon women look for an appropriate subject to impregnate their population. This time the job goes to Dr. Harvey C. Kirk, physics professor and womanizer. They kidnap him and hilarity ensues. It's a sci-fi sex-comedy, minus the sex.

Highlights include: a talentless cast of (mostly) no-names, lots and lots of female bodybuilders in bikinis, CGI and sets that make the SyFy channel look good, a cameo by Michael "Worf" Dorn, footage shot by Ed Wood.


Video: MPEG4 Video (H264), 712x480, 29.970 fps, 1697 Kbps, 01h26m16s
Audio: Dolby AC3, 48000 Hz, stereo, 192 kbps

DVDRip, English audio, no subtitles
